				<div class="EVO"><br><ul><li>Although X. nematophila FliZ shows 56 % identity with Salmonella FliZ , they differ signiﬁcantly from each other in their C-terminal sequences ( data not shown ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21804009" target="_blank">21804009</a>]<br></li>
<li>The FliZ protein shows signiﬁcant homology only with other FliZ proteins from members of the family Enterobacteriaceae .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20889744" target="_blank">20889744</a>]<br></li>
