<li>Wada , T. , Y. Tanabe , and K. Kutsukake , 2011 FliZ acts as a repressor of the ydiV Gene , which encodes an anti-FlhD4C2 factor of the ﬂagellar regulon in Salmonella enterica serovar Typhimu-rium .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=22021388" target="_blank">22021388</a>]<br></li>
