				<div class="SIT"><br><ul><li>As for a possible mechanism , sequence analysis indicates that FliZ shares no similarity to any other known regulator .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=18469103" target="_blank">18469103</a>]<br></li>
<li>This sequence overlaps the putative 35 element of the nlpC promoter and thus may be a plausible target site of FliZ binding .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21804009" target="_blank">21804009</a>]<br></li>
