<li>These data show that FliZ does not act by controlling hilD transcription .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20889744" target="_blank">20889744</a>]<br></li>
<li>Most likely , its effect on SPI1 gene expression is through FliZ .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20833811" target="_blank">20833811</a>]<br></li>
<li>Repression of type 1 ﬁmbrial gene expression by FliZ is through FimZ .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20833811" target="_blank">20833811</a>]<br></li>
<li>We next tested whether FliZ represses type 1 ﬁmbrial gene expression through FimZ .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20833811" target="_blank">20833811</a>]<br></li>
<li>Similarly , RtsB is likely also affecting type 1 ﬁmbrial gene expression through FliZ .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20833811" target="_blank">20833811</a>]<br></li>
